  "description": "Tests ability to find patients who underwent cardiac stress testing (the population for cardiorespiratory fitness assessment). Per PheKB eMERGE Mayo algorithm, the cohort is identified by exercise stress test procedure codes (excluding pharmacologic stress tests).",
